<section class="border-t border-border px-6 py-20 sm:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Transparent pricing</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-text-muted">
        A flat fee on the capital we manage. Prepaid as metered credit — not a revenue share.
        You keep the yield.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card p-8 text-center">
      <div class="flex items-end justify-center gap-2">
        <span class="mono text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight text-accent">2%</span>
        <span class="mb-2 text-lg text-text-muted">/ year</span>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-text-muted">on capital under management · prepaid credit · no profit share</p>

      <div class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-md rounded-lg border border-border bg-bg/40 p-5 text-left text-sm text-text-muted">
        <span class="text-text">Example:</span> stake 100,000 TRX and the annual fee is
        <span class="mono text-text"> 2,000 TRX</span>, drawn from prepaid credit as it accrues.
        Earn the ~15% yield; keep all of it beyond the flat fee.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
